p tier2 planes etc my question is as an unguilded warrior with pretty much the best droppable gear I can buy will I be able to tank in the tier 2 planes without raid gear or will a be a paper tank? I'm only 57 atm but even with the best gear I can buy I have only 3700hp unbuffed ( I'm not sure what that number will be at 60 though? 4000hp maybe? ) <br>
<br>
thnx<br>
